t gave up the dream."],[4129,4291,"But London,"],[4333,4508,"man, London lit the fire under me"],[4508,4654,"and I feel like I found my voice"],[4654,4921,"and it really is full steam ahead."],[4967,5130,"Speaking of London, since you’re"],[5130,5255,"an American writer-director,"],[5255,5355,"will you be making your way back"],[5355,5430,"to Hollywood?"],[5714,5793,"Hollywood."],[5901,5993,"Get out of the country."],[6068,6322,"If I so much as see your name next to"],[6322,6468,"my daughter's in a tabloid,"],[6502,6731,"I will make your life a living hell."],[7019,7086,"Daniel?"]],"38":[[1101,1180,"He's no good at bragging"],[1180,1247,"about himself,"],[1272,1384,"so I'll do it for him."],[1443,1672,"Daniel is a true auteur"],[1693,1830,"and a creative genius."],[1881,1997,"And it was a privilege"],[1997,2114,"to be his leading lady."],[2168,2285,"That's not a light compliment"],[2285,2410,"coming from Emily Blake,"],[2444,2594,"two-time Golden Globe Award winning"],[2594,2811,"actress and celebrated alumni"],[2811,2894,"of the Royal"],[2894,2986,"Shakespeare Company."],[2986,3178,"Well, I've heard that your relationship"],[3178,3307,"wasn't just professional."],[3386,3490,"We'll never tell."],[3816,3870,"Oh my God."],[3870,4008,"Thanks for saving me, Emily."],[4066,4225,"She was practically eye-fucking you."],[4225,4346,"I know, geez."],[4400,4575,"This is so surreal, I mean, I can't believe"],[4575,4692,"this is happening to me."],[4717,4808,"I can."],[4867,4992,"The moment I read your script,"],[4992,5109,"I knew you were special."],[5301,5367,"Daniel,"],[5459,5568,"enjoy this."],[5668,5826,"And get used to compliments."],[5901,6043,"There's already Oscar buzz."],[6043,6118,"Oh fuck."],[6139,6231,"Pinch me, I know."],[6264,6373,"I feel like I'm dreaming."],[6639,6694,"You okay?"],[6777,6923,"You always do that when you're nervous."],[6923,7165,"Yeah, I know, it's an old habit."],[7269,7340,"Well,"],[7386,7515,"the world's about to meet its new"],[7515,7640,"fav